{"tid":311180,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]一人一個對付 cold call 狗嘅方法","createTime":"2017-07-06T11:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T11:47:29.000Z","uid":103325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5eb5a973562d34e1d5751791f1f19f13007de25","tid":311180,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"啱啱收到個 cold call 又手快快接咗<br />\n等佢講完一大輪野之後，同佢講我聽唔清楚，叫佢講多次&hellip;佢講完又叫佢重覆，前後叫佢重覆咗十幾次，佢把聲越來越閪，到佢想屌鳩個陣我就 cut 鳩佢線<br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他方法玩鳩佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd807909d5e376e4158d3e4cf7259e14d9e5897d","tid":311180,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}